Listing.mainHeadline: a home to fill your heart with pride
Listing.mainDescription: lifestyle  an exceptional family residence that will fill your heart with pride, the immaculate ‘engadine’ beautifully combines federation elegance with contemporary style.  privately positioned in a quiet leafy street, a short stroll to harbour and manly beaches, ferry, cafes and cbd buses    accommodation  casual living and gourmet kitchen area flows through bi-folding doors to the majestic rear garden and sandstone entertainer’s terrace with built-in gas bbq.  spacious formal lounge and separate dining.  sunny front terrace with water views.  indulgent master suite, spacious bedrooms and abundant storage throughout    features  magnificent street appeal with its sandstone and original fa?ade, tessellated tile porch, automatic double garage and landscaped gardens.  light and bright with timber floors, leadlight windows, soaring ornate ceilings, central heating, fireplaces and elegant architraves.  massive attic space, potential for second level (STCA)

lifestyle  perched in a sunny elevated position overlooking the beach with views to the cbd, this immaculate family home epitomises first class living.architect-designed in 2004, it is an entertainer’s delight with masses of open plan space, a huge alfresco terrace and poolside bbq patio

lifestyle    surrounded by ocean and harbour beaches and within easy strolling distance to the convenience of manly, this superbly appointed apartment offers the features of a semi without the price tag. full of character and generously proportioned the apartment flows to a sun filled common courtyard and has an exclusive yet extremely large, lower level multifunctional storage area    features    period features including polished floors and ornate ceilings. quality built-ins in both bedrooms, gas heating, internal laundry. a relaxed coastal lifestyle awaits    accommodation    one of only 4 the apartment has a spacious master bedroom with light-filled sunroom, living room flowing to a gourmet galley kitchen which opens out onto the designer courtyard. the second bedroom and sparkling bathroom complete a desirable package
